data.title: Brad Wenzel - 2015 - Baseball
data.meta_description: Brad Wenzel (32) 1B/OF  - 2015: Returns as a team leader ... is a line drive hitter with power ... is smooth around the bag.2014: Second Team All-South
data.text:
2015: Returns as a team leader ... is a line drive hitter with power ... is smooth around the bag.

2014: Second Team All-South Region and First Team All-CAC selection ... played in and started 42 games ... led the team with a .417 batting average and a .634 slugging percentage, while compiling a .462 on-base percentage ... led the team with 73 hits, seven home runs and 111 total bases ... had a 17-game hit streak that stretched from March 22nd to April 18th ... recorded career-highs in hits (5) and RBI (7) against Wesley on April 5th ... hit a career-high two home runs at Scranton on May 3rd ... had a stretch of 14 hits in 19 at-bats with 12 RBI in a four-game span from April 5-10.

2013: Saw action in six games with four starts for the Spartan pitching staff before having his season ended by an arm injury ... went 1-3 with a 5.16 ERA in 29.2 innings ... tossed a career-high eight innings twice against Mt. Aloyisus and Salisbury ... struck out a career-high eight in the March 17 2-1 loss to Salisbury ... opponents hit .276 against him ... struck out 17 and walked 13 during his 29.2 innings ... did not get an at-bat as a pitcher.
